reviews.text: Good food, good service
Food is great, however the downside is that it is quiet far from the MTR stations, need at least a 10minute walk.
Love the iced abalones

Very good local restaurant with awesome homely service :) 

Recommended dishes:
- fried toast with shrimps and apple salad. The apples are sooooo good! The toast is also fried very well. 
- winter melon soup
- pyramid pork belly slices - not too fatty and even has salted veg at the bottom
食物好味，夠獲氣
